-- National Bank of Kuwait to Start Capital Increase Program From October 5
-- Fiona MacDonald
-- 2010-09-07T07:46:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-07/national-bank-of-kuwait-to-start-10-capital-increase-program-from-oct-5.html

          
          
             National Bank of Kuwait SAK, the
country’s biggest lender, will open a subscription period for a
capital raise on Oct. 5 until Oct. 21, the bank said in a
statement to the Kuwait bourse today.  
 NBK shareholders in March approved raising the bank’s
capital by 10 percent to 359.8 million dinars ($1.25 billion).  
